### Signup
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "taylor@example.com",
  "password": "supersecure123",
  "handle": "taylor"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "taylor@example.com",
  "password": "supersecure123"
}

### Set token from login response:
# @name login
# Use VSCode REST Client: set variable `@token={{login.response.body.$.token}}`

### Me
GET http://localhost:4000/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create car
POST http://localhost:4000/cars
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Red Ghost",
  "year": 2020,
  "make": "Dodge",
  "model": "Charger",
  "whp": 520,
  "drivetrain": "RWD"
}

### Get my cars
GET http://localhost:4000/cars
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List venues
GET http://localhost:4000/venues

### List events (all)
GET http://localhost:4000/events

### RSVP to first event (replace :id)
POST http://localhost:4000/events/:id/rsvp
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Check-in (requires your lat/lon inside polygon & current time within event window)
POST http://localhost:4000/events/:id/checkin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lat": 32.5620,
  "lon": -96.9530
}
